---
import ArrowUpRight from '../icons/ArrowUpRight.astro';
---

<section id="cases" class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="shell flex flex-col items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20">
    <h2 class="max-w-[760px] text-left text-[24px] font-semibold leading-[1.4] text-blue-900 lg:text-center lg:text-[32px]">
      Conheça casos reais de empresas que transformaram sua operação comercial com a
      <span class="text-blue-600">Salestime</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="relative flex w-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] bg-gray-50 lg:flex-row lg:items-stretch">
      <!-- Card do case -->
      <div class="flex shrink-0 flex-col justify-between gap-8 rounded-[32px] bg-blue-600 p-8 sm:p-10 lg:h-[441px] lg:w-[531px]">
        <span class="flex size-[50px] shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-lemon text-blue-900">
          <ArrowUpRight class="h-7 w-7" />
        </span>
        <p class="text-[28px] font-medium leading-[1.15] text-white lg:text-[40px]">
          Como a Solvis conquistou + R$ 80K de renda recorrente mensal
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Depoimento -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-9 p-8 sm:p-10 lg:max-w-[525px] lg:py-10 lg:pl-20 lg:pr-16">
        <img
          src="/images/cases/solvis.svg"
          alt="Solvis"
          width="160"
          height="40"
          loading="lazy"
          class="h-10 w-auto self-start"
        />
        <blockquote class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-[1.3] text-blue-900">
          “A partir do diagnóstico da Salestime foi possível entender melhor o
          papel da área de vendas. Reduzimos nosso ciclo, triplicamos o setor e
          passamos a atingir clientes com maiores tickets.”
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="flex items-center gap-[22px]">
          <img
            src="/images/cases/joana.webp"
            alt="Joana Oliveira"
            width="60"
            height="60"
            loading="lazy"
            class="size-[60px] rounded-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900">Joana Oliveira</span>
            <span class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900">Head de Vendas na Solvis</span>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </div>

      <!-- Paginação -->
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 pb-6 lg:absolute lg:bottom-10 lg:right-16 lg:pb-0" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></span>
        <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-gray-200"></span>
        <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-gray-200"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
